name: Available Test Information

children.description: Given User Logs in to Home Page and goes to Modify Order Page
When User Search by lab number "20210000000003761" from previous testing steps on the Modify Oder Page
Then Table headers are correct Under Available Tests
When User Check box next to  several tests
Then Assign test Check boxes stick
When User unCheck box next to  several tests
Then Assign test Check boxes will uncheck
